/Report/*.log

# Runtime generated reports and fetched data
/Report/*.md
/Report/*.html
/data/inbox/news_candidates_*.json
/data/inbox/manual/*.json
/data/inbox/manual/*.json.disabled

# Local editor/system noise
.DS_Store
*.swp
